---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import ImagePlaceholder from '../components/ImagePlaceholder.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about KSM Technology Partners — our mission, values, and the team behind our work.">

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About KSM Technology Partners</h1>
      <p>Engineering-led technology consulting for regulated industries.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          KSM Technology Partners is a technology consulting firm founded on a simple premise: the best technology consulting is done by practitioners who have built real systems in complex environments. Our team consists of engineers, architects, and project leaders with deep hands-on experience — not generalists who specialize in PowerPoint.
        </p>
        <p>
          We focus on two industries where the stakes are high and the technical challenges are genuine: electric utilities and life sciences. These industries share important characteristics — complex operational technology, strict regulatory requirements, large amounts of critical data, and a need to move faster without sacrificing reliability or compliance.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our clients range from regional electric cooperatives to global pharmaceutical manufacturers. What they share is a need for technology partners who understand both the technical challenges and the business context — and who can execute.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <p>
          We are engineers first. We write code, design systems, and work alongside client teams — not above them. We believe that the best way to deliver value is to be embedded in the work, not managing from a distance.
        </p>
        <p>
          We favor pragmatic solutions over fashionable ones. We choose the right tool for the job — sometimes that's the latest cloud-native technology, sometimes it's a well-understood pattern that's been reliable for decades. We're not dogmatic about technology choices, but we are rigorous about engineering quality.
        </p>
        <p>
          We take knowledge transfer seriously. Our engagements are designed to leave client teams more capable than when we started, not more dependent on external consultants.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <ImagePlaceholder caption="KSM Technology Partners team" />

        <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
          <h3>Our Values</h3>
          <ul class="value-list">
            <li>Engineering rigor over convenient shortcuts</li>
            <li>Client capability over consultant dependency</li>
            <li>Honest assessments over comfortable agreement</li>
            <li>Domain depth over generalist breadth</li>
            <li>Long-term relationships over transactional engagements</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Industries -->
  <div class="section-pale">
    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-2">Industries We Serve</h2>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Utilities</h3>
          <p>
            We work with electric, gas, and water utilities on grid modernization, operational technology integration, data platforms, and the regulatory compliance challenges unique to the energy sector — including NERC CIP, FERC compliance, and AMI integration.
          </p>
          <a href="case-studies" class="card-link">View utilities case studies →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🔬</div>
          <h3>Life Sciences</h3>
          <p>
            We work with pharmaceutical manufacturers, biotech companies, medical device firms, and contract research organizations on GxP-compliant software delivery, LIMS integration, clinical data management, and regulatory submission systems.
          </p>
          <a href="case-studies" class="card-link">View life sciences case studies →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cta-banner">
    <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
    <p>Whether you have a specific project in mind or are just exploring options, we'd welcome the conversation.</p>
    <a href="contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contact Us</a>
  </div>

</PageLayout>
